Porter Ranch, and she filed this
report.

43:10.988 --> 43:17.695 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: On the surface, it
seems a serene,
picturesque Southern California
town, with

43:17.728 --> 43:23.367 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
gated communities and views. But
Porter Ranch,
which is home to 30,000
residents in Northern

43:23.401 --> 43:27.138 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
L.A., is anything but serene
