43:27.171 --> 43:33.177 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
An invisible environmental
disaster is unfolding
in the hills above the
community, where natural

43:33.211 --> 43:38.416 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
