underground
gas storage facilities called
Aliso Canyon.

43:43.187 --> 43:47.258 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE CONLEY, University of
California, Davis:
This one leak is roughly
equivalent to the

43:47.291 --> 43:53.231 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
