planes in the
country with specialized
equipment that can

44:03.508 --> 44:07.678 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
measure gas leaks from the air.

44:07.712 --> 44:12.283 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For the last several months,
