44:47.385 --> 44:52.490 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: In recent weeks, as
the Southern
California Gas Company has begun
to drain

44:52.523 --> 44:57.528 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
