Mizrahi.

45:02.166 --> 45:05.236 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But the company is still unclear
why it happened.

45:05.269 --> 45:08.072 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MIKE MIZRAHI, Southern
California Gas Company:
We really won't know what caused
the leak

45:08.105 --> 45:10.408 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
