45:31.562 --> 45:37.201 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: The well causing all
the havoc was
built in 1953. Like other
natural gas wells

45:37.234 --> 45:42.139 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
